Comment: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:29.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Minami not coming today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.14,0:01:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a slacker. Yomogi, get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, why can't you focus?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.02,0:02:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.32,0:02:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it's almost time for work.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.79,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauma, where's Minami?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.58,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she called saying\Nshe had to go meet someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she's stood up a bunch of guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a slacker.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.15,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Minami's meeting someone, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be weird if I asked about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.58,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My impression of Kano?\NIs that what this is about?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.59,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She was super serious\Nwith practice and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.34,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone loved her\N'cuz she was cheerful.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheerful?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.27,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different than the Kano I knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.23,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I think Kano picked out\Nthe song for that recital.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.07,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. I wanted to meet you\Nto learn stuff like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.79,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Sorry I'm not much help.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.09,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I think Urita might have a few videos.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Videos?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.72,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Of chorus practice\Nfor the club records.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.93,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Kano's in 'em a bunch.\NWant his number?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Urita would be happy to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.69,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you going around\Nasking people about Kano?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've always been\Na little curious, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.20,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'll let you know if I\Nthink of something. Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay? Feeling sick?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I that zoned out?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By that look, I'd say you're in love.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.89,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been acting sneaky lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You like someone, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You like someone, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You like someone, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.96,0:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a granny like me went through\Na season or two of love.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a granny?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.51,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Freshman, get with it and\Nmake your move before it's too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask her out on a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A date?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean? Is this like... a date?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit your mumbling over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You were here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Have been since morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet the chorus grad?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.39,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a big girl high-schooler now, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made you change?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not from anyone's influence.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Smirk much?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.16,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be rough working\Nmornings and nights. Poor guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's easy compared to\N5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomogi, is your cold getting worse?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I've gotta go.\NThanks for breakfast.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can skip training today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap, I'm gonna be late.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.19,0:06:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is that fair?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry, hurry! Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, allow me to introduce
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.37,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the exchange students\Ntransferring to our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go figure. He's in our class.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.51,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping for a wonderful\Nexperience in Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.26,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sizumu. For your seat,\Njust take the one behind Minami.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on, I have a few\Nannouncements to make. {put up top?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.90,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't just some coincidence, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's your face red?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's my cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.50,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dynazenon? You guys should know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hidden far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just saw it flying.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna be late!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use it like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.02,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask because I'm curious about you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.89,0:08:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as how I'm an exchange student,\NI hope we can all get along.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure caught me off guard.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His outfit?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.12,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's not here to fight,\Nbut shouldn't we tell Gauma?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know he'd charge right in.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He might.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.67,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys used to get along with Gauma\N5,000 years ago, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, maybe.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This conversation...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can work it out without kaiju.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll appear even if we do.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys make the kaiju?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They grow by people's wills.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eugenicists don't create kaiju.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.87,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to create a world\Nwhere kaiju are needed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not kaiju users, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so,\Nbut Gauma believes we are.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.34,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think\Nyou need to fight kaiju?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep inside, maybe you just\Nwant to fight them?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.14,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. We're just\Ndoing what we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are kaiju born?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.52,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,People may seem free,\Nbut everyone's bound by something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.94,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kaiju that frees them\Nfrom that something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Gauma.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with his outfit?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.54,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you plotting\Nby approaching these guys?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.88,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't a transfer student make friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, my ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slug you in the kisser!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slug you! I'll slug you so hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for it, bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, I came to see someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You've got all it wrong! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Would you behave?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go! I can explain myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.95,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell was Sizumu thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.74,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He can hear kaijus' voices,\Nso perhaps he has a plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.67,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I add the savory white custard?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cold for sure. Stay home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.93,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't. Ugh, my head hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.19,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! You want to\Nspread it to everyone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you're so loud!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you okay after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.28,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They reported you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I got fired from my job.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.08,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got screwed. Next time,\NI'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yomogi?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's got a nasty cold.\NProbably won't be coming for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be bad if a kaiju came?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally want that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gauma. I need a day off next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every day off!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume, check up on Yomogi after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the point if it's just a cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.65,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomogi's been slacking lately\Nlike his heart isn't in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that my problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.53,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't made him wait in the rain,\Nhe wouldn't be sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a kaiju.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird one. Strange power.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't zoned out like this in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Freshman, get with it and\Nmake your move before it's too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ask her out on a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Date...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When she's like that,\Nit ain't easy for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.86,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here to visit?! How nice of you to come!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.03,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the tone of her voice,\NI bet it's just Gauma.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You're sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I bought all this stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Comment: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:03.93,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's trippy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very kaiju-like power.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it shifts dimensions.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Go for it, Mujina!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Instance Domination.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauma said I should check up on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.34,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You have stuff you don't want seen?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. No.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you told jokes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Just what do you take me for?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we only started talking recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.85,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Gauma that you couldn't\Ncome to training the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.44,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz you were meeting someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A chorus club grad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chorus club?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for your sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.12,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew a bit about her,\Nbut it wasn't like they knew her well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.29,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But they put me in touch\Nwith someone. A guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. F-Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Gauma.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yume! Come quick with Dyna Wing!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... you're in no shape to help.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But—!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Dyna Soldier?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.69,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We gotta do everything we can.\NBefore it's too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. We'll have someone pilot it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Access Mode... Dyna Striker!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Access Mode... Dyna Diver!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna work!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd it go through, dammit?!\NWhere's Yume?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.22,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauma, Yomogi's too sick to fight.\NI brought Dyna Soldier instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't combine without a pilot for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my time to shine!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-When did you—?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.28,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise Asukagawa will pilot Dyna Soldier!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who said it's up to you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.33,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Access Mode... Dyna Soldier!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it! I really did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine and fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you, Chise?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If I think of it as a game!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened to combining?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could, but...!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush the little one, Mujina!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bossing me around!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chise! Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me go to another memorial.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep inside, maybe you just\Nwant to fight them? {italicize?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes you think\Nyou need to fight kaiju?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, Minami?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Real ugly.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I should come.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We might need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that, how do I get there?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I can borrow Mom's car.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomogi, hop in!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only buy her so much time!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise, let's switch!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'd appreciate it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dyna Soldier Wing Combine!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yomo, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm far from okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's combine!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.78,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine Dragon Dynazenon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...Battle, Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Beam!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Penetrator Gun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mujina, focus!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shouting doesn't help!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Burst Missile Kick!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,150)}Achoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1600,150)}Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,136)}Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.47,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Dragon Dyna Rex!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.97,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Up you go! Heave ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazing Inferno...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.98,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rex Roar!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.46,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Gauma!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.04,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.36,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver, Yomo! I'll do my best\Nto train as your Dyna Soldier backup!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't have to.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}By next week, I'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! I'll combine by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you can do it, I can, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How rude.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.16,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynazenon... Can anyone pilot you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a ride?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming to get me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've brought you along\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come along next time?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.14,0:21:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.27,0:21:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go asking about your sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but why?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know more about you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.83,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stand! Bow!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.21,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, don't forget that your second period\Nwill be in the language lab today. Also—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.97,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I caught it.
